description._content: Description: Northern Range. Self-sown Cypress coming in, under Aleppo Pine. Kartaldagh Forest. Location: Kartaldagh, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Description: Northern Range. Aleppo Pine sown, and natural regeneration. Kartaldagh Forest. Location: Kartaldagh, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/697 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
